OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fis at a tipping point, the chief
OL,8,Fconstable has warned.
OL,10,FJon Boutcher detailed additional
OL,11,Fduties being taken on, including
OL,12,Fplugging a gap where the Northern
OL,13,FIreland Ambulance Service cannot
OL,14,Fattend calls, and said without the
OL,15,Fnecessary funding they will have to
OL,16,Ftake some "difficult decisions" on
OL,17,Fwhat they can do.
OL,19,FHe was speaking as the recently
OL,20,Frestored Northern Ireland Executive
OL,21,Fprepares to set the next budget.
