OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FLast week the Assembly's justice
OL,7,Fcommittee heard a warning that this is
OL,8,Fset to be a "most challenging year"
OL,9,Ffor the Department of Justice which
OL,10,Ffunds the PSNI, and is facing
OL,11,F#444million of pressures.
OL,13,FAppearing before the Northern Ireland
OL,14,FPolicing Board on Thursday, Mr
OL,15,FBoutcher outlined an example of an
OL,16,Felderly woman with a broken pelvis who
OL,17,Fwas brought to hospital in a police
OL,18,FLand Rover because no ambulances were
OL,19,Favailable.
