OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FHe referred to the Patten report on
OL,7,Fpolicing which recommended 7,500 full-
OL,8,Ftime officers in a peacetime Northern
OL,9,FIreland, but said they have lost 22%
OL,10,Fwith numbers currently at 6,400.
OL,12,FThe chief constable said while the
OL,13,Fthreat level was lowered from severe
OL,14,Fto substantial this week, it has
OL,15,F"effectively been at severe since
OL,16,F2010".
