OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,F"This a unique place with regards to
OL,7,Fpolicing in the United Kingdom, we are
OL,8,Fthe glue that holds the Good Friday
OL,9,FAgreement in place and we need to be a
OL,10,Fservice that is capable of attracting
OL,11,Fand sustaining support from the
OL,12,Fcommunity as a whole," he said.
OL,14,F"The service, in real terms, we have
OL,15,Flost 22% of our staffing levels in
OL,16,Fpolice officers. That is not
OL,17,Fsustainable."
