OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FMr Boutcher contended that the PSNI
OL,7,Fhas experienced the largest
OL,8,Fexpenditure reduction in all the UK
OL,9,Fpolice forces since 2010, and the
OL,10,Fbudget of the Garda Siochana in the
OL,11,FRepublic of Ireland has gone up 23% in
OL,12,Fthe last three years.
OL,14,FHe also described sickness levels as
OL,15,Fhaving risen "significantly" to double
OL,16,Flevels in England and Wales, while
OL,17,Fstaff morale last year faltered.
