OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FMr Boutcher said the PSNI had positive
OL,7,Freports from His Majesty's
OL,8,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,9,F& Rescue Services (HMICFRS), the
OL,10,FIndependent Reporting Commission and
OL,11,Fthe Northern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,12,Fbut also expressed concern around
OL,13,Fstaffing levels and/or budget.
OL,15,FHe said the HMICFRS report recognised
OL,16,Fthe additional responsibilities of
OL,17,Fpolice in Northern Ireland, including
OL,18,Fnational threats, legacy, being an
OL,19,Farmed force, a fortified estate and
OL,20,Fthreats against officers.
