OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,FIn terms of supporting the health
OL,7,Fservice, Mr Boutcher said police
OL,8,Fattend around 500 ambulance calls a
OL,9,Fmonths, where the ambulance service
OL,10,Fcannot respond to calls.
OL,12,FHe said between January 1, 2023 and
OL,13,FApril 14, 2023 police spent
OL,14,Fapproximately 4,550 hours in hospitals
OL,15,Fwith people in a mental health crisis,
OL,16,Fand between March 1, 2023 and March 1,
OL,17,F2024 police dealt with 21,425 calls
OL,18,Frelating to mental health.
