OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,F"This is the tip of the iceberg. There
OL,7,Fis an example in my foreword where our
OL,8,Farmed response officers managed to
OL,9,Flook after an elderly lady who was in
OL,10,Fcrisis and simply couldn't get an
OL,11,Fambulance... we removed her in an
OL,12,Farmoured Land Rover with her daughter.
OL,13,FThese are day-to-day examples," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"It's getting to a position where if
OL,17,Fwe don't get the support that we need,
OL,18,Fwe will be having some really
OL,19,Fdifficult conversations about what we
OL,20,Fare and what we are not able to do.
