OL,3,CPSNI at tipping point, chief constable
OL,4,Cwarns
OL,6,F"The situation is pretty serious...
OL,7,Ftipping point is exactly where we are,
OL,8,Fso I would appeal to anybody and
OL,9,Feverybody understands the challenges
OL,10,Fthat we are facing, conscious of the
OL,11,Fincredible difficulty facing other
OL,12,Fpublic services and the amount of
OL,13,Ffunding provided to Northern Ireland,
OL,14,Fbut recognises the need for policing
OL,15,Fto be invested in."
